http://www.w3.org/TR/UNDERSTANDING-WCAG20/visual-audio-contrast-contrast.html#visual-audio-contrast-contrast-resources-head

errors.message: Header nesting - header following h1 is incorrect.
errors.solution: Modify the header levels so only an h1 or h2 follows h1.
